# qmd/ALCHEMY

Local helper-script utility belt around the main ALCHEMY pipeline. The canonical pipeline definition lives elsewhere — start there for any real workflow question.

Start here for orientation:
- `SKILL.md` — this folder's reading order and workflow map.
- `/projects/BURROWS/akashgpt/run_scripts/ALCHEMY__dev` — active development copy (`$ALCHEMY__dev`).
- `/projects/BURROWS/akashgpt/run_scripts/ALCHEMY__in_use` — stable copy (`$ALCHEMY__main`).

Note: `mldp` is no longer a standalone repo. It lives under `ALCHEMY__dev/TRAIN_MLMD_scripts/ANALYSIS/mldp` (and the parallel path under `ALCHEMY__in_use`, available as `$ALCHEMY__main__MLDP` / `$ALCHEMY__dev__MLDP`; see `sys/myshortcuts.sh`). The `mldp_ALCHEMY` symlink in this folder points to the dev copy for convenience.
